n: Finger Lickin' Rock and Roll Artichokes
des: "This is the best artichoke dip you will ever taste in your whole life. The secret is in the seasonings. The tasty blend of Parmesan and Monterey Jack cheeses doesn't hurt, either!"
ins: In a medium bowl, mix together artichoke hearts, mayonnaise, Parmesan cheese, Monterey Jack cheese, garlic powder, seasoning salt, soy sauce and hot pepper sauce. Chill in the refrigerator until serving.
